Notice on Multiple Contributors
================================

This repository includes contributions from more than one author. Git
history shows a second contributor, GitHub user CLOR2003, alongside
repository owner Daniel Leone (GitHub: dagron27).

Based on the commit history, CLOR2003 authored substantially all of the
content of `seed_analysis_dbscan.ipynb` (originally committed as
`seed_analysis.ipynb`), contributed via a series of "Created using Colab"
commits. Daniel Leone authored the repository scaffolding (README,
.gitignore, dataset files and `dataset/converter.py`, requirements.txt, CI
workflow) and substantially all of `seed_analysis_k_means.ipynb`, plus an
early scaffold and one conflict-resolution pass on the DBSCAN notebook.

No permission has been obtained from CLOR2003 to relicense their
contributions. Accordingly, the MIT License terms below apply only to the
portions of this Software authored by Daniel Leone. CLOR2003's
contributions (principally the contents of `seed_analysis_dbscan.ipynb`)
are included in this repository for archival and portfolio purposes only,
remain the property of their author, and are NOT relicensed, granted, or
warranted under this or any other license by this notice. Anyone wishing
to use, copy, modify, or distribute CLOR2003's contributions must obtain
permission directly from CLOR2003.

